            <h1 class="blog-post_title">Center Base Literacy</h1>
            <p class="blog-post_text">Organized classes from 2002 to 2007 (Center Base Literacy) which was run with the help of SRC, JAMIA MILLIA ISLAMIA UNIVERSITY. There were 20 or sometimes 25 centers in this program. For these study centers, SRC JAMIA MILLIA ISLAMIA used to provide us with books. In other activities, self-help groups were made available to the learners about which they were given training on Vocational Course so that they could help themselves. These vocational courses benefited them a lot, due to which their financial condition became good. These vocational courses include cutting, tailoring, weaving, and hand embroidery, and the art of making refills for pens.</p>
        </div>
