            <h1 class="blog-post_title1">RAJ MAZDOOR PROGRAM</h1>
            <p class="blog-post_text1">Under this program, workers working in construction work were given literacy classes. Wherever we find 15 to 20 workers working in the building, we go there and conduct classes after they finish their work, at night time they study and along with their studies, we also taught them how to withdraw money from the bank, post office and send money and fill the withdrawal form themselves so that they can be self-dependent.</p>
