            <p class="blog-post_text1">Vikalp Trust got the project of SARVA SHIKSHA ABHIYAN program with the help of Delhi government, we have run 30 centers through this program about 900 illiterate are made literate, and these students are those who never went to school. Along with studying Vocational Course, technical classes were also given by the Trust with its own efforts, in which Motor Winding, Cutting, Tailoring House Wiring, etc are taught. These courses made them self-dependent; all of them were get certified from Sharmik Vidyapeeth Delhi Government.</p>
