            <p class="blog-post_text1">Together with our volunteers, active workers, learners, and parents, we took out a rally of about 5 kilometers in the area of Jamia Nagar in which officers of rotary club south, DCP of Delhi Police South Delhi, officers of Jamia Nagar Thana and SARV SIKSHA ABHYAN, officers of Shramik Vidyapeeth RK Puram. This rally was organized in collaboration with the officials of RK PURAM and the staff of Jamia Millia Islamia University. The purpose of this rally was to bring awareness among the people about the fallout of education. About 7000 people took part in this rally.</p>
