            <p class="blog-post_text1">Hunar program of NIOS was run from 1-11-2013 to 2015. The Hunar program was run in the area of Jamia Nagar; this program was also run in other areas of Delhi like Seelampur, Ballimaran, Zafarabad, and Bara Hindu Rao, etc. In the area of Jamia Nagar, 30 skill centers were opened. The responsibility for running the center in this area was given to the Vikalp trust. Vikalp Trust went from house to house and talked to the people and told them the benefits of the hunar program. And we convenience the public by telling them the goodness of the skill program. People gave us free space and getting this space was a very difficult task. After meeting with the RWAs, NGOs, and social workers of the area, with help, the center was established. The material that was needed for the center, was also arrangedby the community of the instructor in the skill center.</p>
